Service Description: Brief description of the services provided.
Service Category: Category of the services (e.g., Cloud Hosting, Security Services).
Criticality (DORA): Assessment of whether the service is deemed critical under DORA.
Rationale for Criticality: Explanation of why the service is considered critical.
Primary Contact: Contact details of the primary point of contact at the provider.
Contract Start Date: Date the contract began.
